  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Part Time Basketball Coaches",
  "description": "<p>2xSG is looking for <strong>passionate Part-Time Basketball Coaches</strong> to work with youth players across our academies, teams, and leagues.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Conduct basketball training sessions for youth players</p></li><li><p>Support player development, teamwork, and discipline</p></li><li><p>Assist during games, leagues, and tournaments when required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strong basketball background (playing or coaching)</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills and positive attitude</p></li><li><p>Reliable and good with kids/teens</p></li><li><p>Coaching experience preferred (not mandatory)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Commitment</strong></p><ul><li><p>Part-time (weekday late-afternoons and/or weekends)</p></li></ul><p><strong>About 2xSG</strong><br /><br />2xSG is a basketball management and operations group that runs the largest basketball ecosystem in Singapore. We manage all assets and operations of <strong>SG Basketball, FastBreak Singapore, FastBreak KL, FastBreak Johor</strong>, overseeing 50+ youth teams, thousands of students, and multiple adult leagues.<br /><br />Our footprint includes a privately-owned dedicated basketball training facility, the largest youth basketball league in Singapore (over 2,000 players every Sunday), and the largest youth basketball tournament in Southeast Asia (over 200 teams). Our mission is to build better players, stronger teams, and a sustainable basketball pathway across the region.<br /><br /><strong>📩 </strong><em><strong>Interested?</strong></em><br /><br /><strong>Send your name, basketball experience, and availability to chris@2xsg.com.</strong></p>",
